name: ToothFoot: Quest for The Infinity Burger
name_original: ToothFoot: Quest for The Infinity Burger
description:
Toothfoot is just your average girl who has teeth for feet and a everlasting and all consuming hunger for burgers. While out to fill her unquenchable hunger she is told about the infinity burger.  A burger that will finally end her hunger.
